urdu transliteration text:
Aa Ay Mere Husayn Meri Godh Me AajaAaja Mere Bachche Meri Aaghosh Me Aaja
COME, MY SON, COME INTO MY ARMS
@HujjatELC

Aakar Mere Zaanu Pe Jo Sojaate Thay BetaChakki Ki Mashakhat Pe Bhi Pehlu Nahi BadlaAb Kaise Tujhe Chhor Doo Makhtal May Akela
@HujjatELC
Aa Ay Mere Hussain Mere Godh May Aaja- Oh my Hussain Come into my lap
